ional_baseball_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chinese_Taipei_national_baseball_team\"}, {\"begin\": 2463, \"end\": 2469, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Turkey_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9308770587303882, \"rank\": 0.07425571413176846, \"text\": \"Turkey\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Turkey_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Turkey_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 2477, \"end\": 2483, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Taj_al-Din_Yildiz\", \"score\": 0.9999999999990905, \"rank\": 1.1398280041574623e-12, \"text\": \"Yildiz\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Taj_al-Din_Yildiz\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Taj_al-Din_Yildiz\"}, {\"begin\": 2484, \"end\": 2492, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kahraman_(album)\", \"score\": 0.9101295171701695, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Kahraman\", \"types\": [\"Q482994\", \"Q386724\", \"Q2188189\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kahraman_(album)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kahraman_(album)\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Here's what the Brit had to say after his silver medal:  \\\"I did not even know they were here!\\\"\", \"from\": 2515, \"to\": 2609, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00f0\\u009f\\u0098\\u0086Matthew Hudson-Smith had quite the surprise after winning silver in the 400m final!\", \"from\": 2610, \"to\": 2697, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00f0\\u009f\\u00a4\\u0097#BBCOlympics#Olympics#Paris2024pic.twitter.com/StZ3nOts8c  It's a new Olympic record from Jamaica's Roje Stona to take a surprise gold and win the men's discus gold.\", \"from\": 2698, \"to\": 2867, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2792, \"end\": 2799, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jamaica\", \"score\": 0.9999998355897468, \"rank\": 1.6440433394807417e-07, \"text\": \"Jamaica\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jamaica\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jamaica\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Lithuania's world record holder Mykolas Alekna with the silver and Australia's Matthew Denny in bronze.\", \"from\": 2869, \"to\": 2972, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2869, \"end\": 2878, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lithuania_men's_national_basketball_team\", \"score\": 0.9999999331485037, \"rank\": 6.685125537939366e-08, \"text\": \"Lithuania\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lithuania_men's_national_basketball_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lithuania_men's_national_basketball_team\"}, {\"begin\": 2901, \"end\": 2915, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mykolas_Alekna\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Mykolas Alekna\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mykolas_Alekna\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mykolas_Alekna\"}, {\"begin\": 2936, \"end\": 2945, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia_national_rugby_union_team\", \"score\": 0.6280888017893251, \"rank\": 0.5777329393836838, \"text\": \"Australia\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia_national_rugby_union_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia_national_rugby_union_team\"}, {\"begin\": 2948, \"end\": 2961, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Matthew_Denny\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Matthew Denny\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Matthew_Denny\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Matthew_Denny\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Back to the track and it's 3000m Steeplechase gold for Soufiane El Bakkali who successfully defends his title.\", \"from\": 2974, \"to\": 3084, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3029, \"end\": 3048, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Soufiane_El_Bakkali\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": 